<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Until I read Cari&apos;s response, my default answer was, siblings. But unanswered and mysterious as it&apos;s left, Cari could be right. I think the ambiguity <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Until I read Cari's response, my default answer was, siblings. But unanswered and mysterious as it's left, Cari could be right. I think the ambiguity is part of the beauty of this wonderful book. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
